metadata.name: Saddleback Leather Charter Member #1
metadata.description: 2023 will mark the Saddleback 20th Anniversary. To celebrate the next chapter, we released a limited number of NFTs that grant one year of free access to the Saddleback VIP Membership at the Classic Level. The 20 charter members will be historically listed at the Saddleback Headquarters with their names burned on leather. Membership perks will include a $300 “members only” bag, 50 leather business cards with personal emails on them, live Q&A’s with Dave, and more. Full list of benefits coming in 2023. Membership Perks are not transferable.
